sentences.sentence: Detainees complained of being given inedible food.
sentences.translation: 被拘押者抱怨所给的食物不能吃。

sentences.sentence: They don't waste their time on some inedible thing from their point of view.
sentences.translation: 他们不会为不能吃的东西浪费时间，从他们的角度来看。

sentences.sentence: But many Africans and Asians who snack on insects consider shellfish inedible.
sentences.translation: 但许多把昆虫当零食吃的非洲人和亚洲人却认为贝类不能吃。
